ty for what it is and accept the honest facts of the situation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Step 3: Be flexible in the way you close the gap between 1 and 2.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bold. Rational. Adaptable.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-2-quotes-from-others\">2 QUOTES FROM OTHERS<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>I.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Painter&nbsp;<strong>Agnes Martin<\/strong><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong>on the one thing you have to know in life:<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;There are so many people who don\u2019t know what they want. And I think that, in this world, that\u2019s the only thing you have to know \u2014 exactly what you want.&#8221;<span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><br><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source:&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.brainpickings.org\/2013\/03\/22\/agnes-martin-1997-interview\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Interview with Agnes Martin<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>II.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Writer<strong>&nbsp;Audre Lorde&nbsp;<\/strong>on facing our challenges:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Sometimes we are blessed with being able to choose the time, and the arena, and the manner of our revolution, but more usually we must do battle where we are standing.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source:&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/1580911862\/ref=as_li_qf_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=jamesclearema-20&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=1580911862&amp;linkId=01f4fbcc61486d7c73685fdd90d12cf5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sister Outsider: Essays and Speeches<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Am I being effective or just busy?<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Until next week,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Clear<br><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">Author of the million-copy bestseller,&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\/\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\">Atomic Habits<\/a><br><\/em><